Description
Haier Electrical Appliances Indonesia has 27 years of presenting high quality products to consumers and has become the No. 1 Brand for Major Household Equipment in the world , with 78 % of the retail stocks in 2011 . In 2012 , Haier took the initiative to collaborate with Sanyo , and PT Sanyo Indonesia, which is located in Cikarang , Bekasi , West Java , has become part of the Haier Group , to turn into Haier Electrical Appliances Indonesia. Currently we are looking for dedicated and dynamic individuals to join our team as : Material Purchasing Staff
Requirements
Male/Female Maximum age 30 years old Bachelor/Diploma degree from reputable university with any major
Proficiency in English both oral and written is a must
Having experience minimal 1 years as Purchasing Staff and preferably in Manufacturing/Electric Company
Computer literate, familiar with Microsoft Office application is a must
Good communication skills
Willing to stay around Cikarang (Cikarang, Bekasi, Karawang, Cikampek, Purwakarta)
All applications will be treated confidentially & only short listed candidates will be notified
Please click "Apply Now" button to apply
